1
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:14,958
[KUKURI]
Water Impact.

2
00:00:20,625 --> 00:00:22,083
[KIRIHA grunts]

3
00:00:34,708 --> 00:00:36,166
[CHISATO]
Oh, no.

4
00:00:43,166 --> 00:00:45,416
[KUKURI]
Hm...?

5
00:00:45,500 --> 00:00:49,708
What do you think of it? This is
my greatest defense technique.

6
00:00:49,791 --> 00:00:53,000
Wall Weave.
Shelter formation.

7
00:00:53,083 --> 00:00:54,958
[NARRATOR]
Malison Cleanser:

8
00:00:55,041 --> 00:00:58,791
The title given to an exorcist
of supernatural phenomena,

9
00:00:58,875 --> 00:01:01,791
chosen by the local god
of each region.

10
00:02:34,708 --> 00:02:36,708
[KAZUYA]
"Trials of the Local God."

11
00:02:40,166 --> 00:02:42,208
[KUKURI]
The Shelter Formation.

12
00:02:42,291 --> 00:02:45,833
I didn't realize you could
wield eight obi at once.

13
00:02:45,916 --> 00:02:49,541
But doing so has clearly
taken its toll on you.

14
00:02:52,500 --> 00:02:56,541
[KAZUYA]
Ah! Kiriha! You're tiny now.

15
00:02:56,625 --> 00:03:00,458
[KUKURI] You're in no shape
to block a second Water Impact.

16
00:03:00,541 --> 00:03:02,458
Will you reconsider my offer?

17
00:03:02,541 --> 00:03:05,208
[KIRIHA]
I will not!

18
00:03:05,291 --> 00:03:06,750
Kiriha, I...!

19
00:03:06,833 --> 00:03:11,583
Kazuya. If I should fall in this
battle, then do as she says.

20
00:03:11,666 --> 00:03:13,583
There's no point
if you die, too.

21
00:03:13,666 --> 00:03:15,458
What do you mean?

22
00:03:15,541 --> 00:03:17,500
[KUKURI]
O noble white mountain peaks.

23
00:03:17,583 --> 00:03:20,000
Let's give up now.
It's not so bad.

24
00:03:20,083 --> 00:03:22,625
I just have to do
this malison cleansing.

25
00:03:22,708 --> 00:03:24,041
I refuse.

26
00:03:24,125 --> 00:03:27,125
[KUKURI] Gush forth
with a blessed torrent.

27
00:03:27,208 --> 00:03:29,625
But why are you
so against this?

28
00:03:29,708 --> 00:03:33,666
Because... it goes against
the reason I'm here.

29
00:03:35,208 --> 00:03:36,833
Wall Weave!

30
00:03:38,458 --> 00:03:40,208
[KUKURI]
Water Impact.

31
00:03:45,708 --> 00:03:48,083
[KIRIHA grunts]

32
00:03:48,166 --> 00:03:50,916
[KIRIHA]
It's no good. I'm faltering.

33
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:55,416
[KIRIHA]
Forgive me, Kanaka.

34
00:03:55,500 --> 00:03:56,625
--[KIRIHA sighs]
--Kiriha.

35
00:03:56,708 --> 00:03:59,166
[KIRIHA]
I broke my promise.

36
00:03:59,250 --> 00:04:00,791
[KAZUYA gasps, yelps]

37
00:04:04,666 --> 00:04:08,041
[KANAKA]
Hey. Hey!

38
00:04:08,125 --> 00:04:10,000
[KAZUYA groans]

39
00:04:10,083 --> 00:04:11,875
'Sup, kid!

40
00:04:11,958 --> 00:04:16,500
[KAZUYA] Uh... Who are you?
And where the heck am I?

41
00:04:16,583 --> 00:04:20,583
We were fighting this goddess,
and then got engulfed in water.

42
00:04:20,666 --> 00:04:25,125
Yup, that Kukuri's Water Impact
is no joke. She's a tough lady.

43
00:04:25,208 --> 00:04:28,625
Between you and me, Kiriha
doesn't know when she's beat.

44
00:04:28,708 --> 00:04:30,666
Pickin' a fight with
a water goddess...

45
00:04:30,750 --> 00:04:33,166
She's in way over her head!

46
00:04:33,250 --> 00:04:34,708
Ha! Ya get it?

47
00:04:34,791 --> 00:04:37,666
[KANAKA laughs]

48
00:04:37,750 --> 00:04:39,791
[KANAKA]
Wait.

49
00:04:39,875 --> 00:04:42,541
I should go. Gotta get
back to drowning, so...

50
00:04:42,625 --> 00:04:45,791
Just listen. I need
to ask ya for a favor.

51
00:04:45,875 --> 00:04:47,875
What is it?

52
00:04:47,958 --> 00:04:49,625
[KANAKA] 
Save Kiriha for me.

53
00:04:49,708 --> 00:04:52,375
[KAZUYA] You want
me to save her?

54
00:04:52,458 --> 00:04:54,041
What, from that water god?

55
00:04:54,125 --> 00:04:56,625
Not really. See, those two
shouldn't even be fighting

56
00:04:56,708 --> 00:04:58,750
right now. Kiriha's stuck
keeping her end

57
00:04:58,833 --> 00:05:01,166
of a deal she made way back.

58
00:05:01,250 --> 00:05:04,375
What kind of deal? And how
can I get her out of it?

59
00:05:04,458 --> 00:05:06,291
[KANAKA laughs]
Pretty easily.

60
00:05:06,375 --> 00:05:07,791
[KAZUYA]
Uh...

61
00:05:07,875 --> 00:05:10,833
Just get strong! Then you won't
need Kiriha's protection.

62
00:05:10,916 --> 00:05:13,291
You can start
protecting her instead!

63
00:05:13,375 --> 00:05:14,916
But that's completely insane!

64
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:17,208
The heck it is!
We'll start by teaching you

65
00:05:17,291 --> 00:05:20,583
what you need to know to
get out of this predicament.

66
00:05:20,666 --> 00:05:22,125
[KAZUYA]
Eh...?

67
00:05:24,541 --> 00:05:29,333
So, I... use her true name, and
wait for an ultimate attack?

68
00:05:29,416 --> 00:05:32,166
That's it! Sounds like you
can handle things from here.

69
00:05:32,250 --> 00:05:33,500
Break a leg.

70
00:05:33,583 --> 00:05:37,083
[KAZUYA] Wait a sec.
What is Kiriha's true name?

71
00:05:37,166 --> 00:05:42,166
You already know it.
Good luck, Kazuya.

72
00:05:42,250 --> 00:05:43,708
[KAZUYA]
Uh...

73
00:05:48,291 --> 00:05:49,750
[KAZUYA]
Mm...

74
00:05:52,125 --> 00:05:54,500
[KIRIHA]
Are you all right?

75
00:05:54,583 --> 00:05:57,083
[KUKURI]
You're quite resilient.

76
00:05:57,166 --> 00:06:00,958
But I won't allow you
time to recuperate.

77
00:06:01,041 --> 00:06:02,250
Do your worst, then.

78
00:06:02,333 --> 00:06:05,125
No, hold on! Just change
back into an obi for me.

79
00:06:05,208 --> 00:06:07,291
Let me wield you, okay?

80
00:06:07,375 --> 00:06:08,541
Let you what?

81
00:06:08,625 --> 00:06:10,625
You're too weak to fight
on your own now, right?

82
00:06:10,708 --> 00:06:12,125
Let me help.

83
00:06:12,208 --> 00:06:15,625
That's ridiculous. I will not
be wielded by my servant.

84
00:06:17,083 --> 00:06:18,875
I, Kazuya Kagami,
command you.

85
00:06:18,958 --> 00:06:20,375
[KIRIHA]
Ah--!

86
00:06:20,458 --> 00:06:23,041
Take on your true form,
Ayasakura.

87
00:06:23,125 --> 00:06:25,291
[KIRIHA gasps]

88
00:06:25,375 --> 00:06:26,458
[KAZUYA]
Ahh!

89
00:06:26,541 --> 00:06:28,291
[KUKURI gasps]

90
00:06:28,375 --> 00:06:30,208
[KIRIHA] Where did you learn
to use true names like that?

91
00:06:30,291 --> 00:06:31,958
Do you have any idea
what you've done?

92
00:06:32,041 --> 00:06:34,041
Now you'll be the one
that has to battle Kukuri!

93
00:06:34,125 --> 00:06:37,500
[KAZUYA grunts repeatedly]

94
00:06:37,583 --> 00:06:40,416
Yeah, but I'll have
you with me.

95
00:06:40,500 --> 00:06:43,416
[KIRIHA] You fool.
Know your place.

96
00:06:43,500 --> 00:06:46,166
[KAZUYA] This is the only way.
You're out of strength.

97
00:06:46,250 --> 00:06:49,291
[KIRIHA]
Uh... Have you a strategy?

98
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:53,666
I do.

99
00:06:53,750 --> 00:06:54,833
[KIRIHA]
Very well.

100
00:06:54,916 --> 00:06:57,250
[KUKURI] A plan born
from desperation.

101
00:06:57,333 --> 00:07:00,041
You must know that
it's doomed to fail.

102
00:07:05,291 --> 00:07:06,333
[KUKURI]
Water Pressure.

103
00:07:06,416 --> 00:07:07,916
[KIRIHA]
It comes!

104
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:09,666
[KAZUYA]
Shield Weave!

105
00:07:09,750 --> 00:07:10,750
Eh--?

106
00:07:10,833 --> 00:07:13,958
[KAZUYA yelps]

107
00:07:14,041 --> 00:07:15,125
Uh... Whoopsie.

108
00:07:15,208 --> 00:07:17,041
[KIRIHA]
That was pathetic!

109
00:07:17,125 --> 00:07:19,083
I'll get it right next time!

110
00:07:20,208 --> 00:07:21,791
[KUKURI]
Water Wheel.

111
00:07:24,125 --> 00:07:25,791
[KAZUYA grunts]

112
00:07:27,333 --> 00:07:29,500
--Did I--?
--[KIRIHA] You did!

113
00:07:29,583 --> 00:07:33,833
See that, Kukuri?
Behold my servant's prowess!

114
00:07:33,916 --> 00:07:36,333
[KUKURI]
He is learning quickly.

115
00:07:36,416 --> 00:07:41,583
Now let us see if he can
stand against my true power.

116
00:07:41,666 --> 00:07:43,708
O noble white mountain peaks.

117
00:07:43,791 --> 00:07:46,000
Gush forth with
a blessed torrent.

118
00:07:46,083 --> 00:07:48,916
Let your fury be known
to the world below.

119
00:07:51,625 --> 00:07:53,041
[KIRIHA] This attack is
larger than the ones

120
00:07:53,125 --> 00:07:57,916
that preceded it. If it hits
us directly, we're finished.

121
00:07:58,000 --> 00:08:01,000
Show me how you wield
an obi, Kazuya.

122
00:08:01,083 --> 00:08:02,250
[KAZUYA gasps]

123
00:08:02,333 --> 00:08:03,583
Right!

124
00:08:03,666 --> 00:08:07,041
[KUKURI] Flowing serpent,
heed my will.

125
00:08:08,750 --> 00:08:10,833
[KUKURI]
Twisting Water Wyrm!

126
00:08:10,916 --> 00:08:12,375
[KAZUYA groans]

127
00:08:15,458 --> 00:08:17,875
[KIRIHA]
What now?

128
00:08:17,958 --> 00:08:20,625
I can guarantee ya that Kukuri's
gonna try to finish you off

129
00:08:20,708 --> 00:08:24,625
with a water snake. Here's what
ya do when she tries it.

130
00:08:24,708 --> 00:08:26,333
[KAZUYA]
Obi Shield Weave!

131
00:08:28,250 --> 00:08:31,583
[KIRIHA] You fool! A single
shield won't be nearly enough!

132
00:08:35,458 --> 00:08:36,916
Watershed!

133
00:08:40,083 --> 00:08:41,541
[KUKURI]
Impossible!

134
00:08:46,750 --> 00:08:49,166
Spiral Weave!

135
00:08:49,250 --> 00:08:51,958
[KUKURI]
Frozen Water Curtain.

136
00:08:52,041 --> 00:08:53,583
[KIRIHA] 
We can't pierce that.

137
00:08:53,666 --> 00:08:55,291
Layered Edge!

138
00:09:01,291 --> 00:09:03,750
[KIRIHA]
This technique...

139
00:09:03,833 --> 00:09:07,416
[KAZUYA yells]

140
00:09:18,416 --> 00:09:23,208
[KAZUYA groans. gasps]

141
00:09:23,291 --> 00:09:24,583
[KAZUYA]
Kiriha!

142
00:09:24,666 --> 00:09:26,541
[KUKURI]
An impressive performance.

143
00:09:26,625 --> 00:09:32,083
You came surprisingly close,
but in the end, I am a god.

144
00:09:32,166 --> 00:09:34,000
Now then.

145
00:09:34,083 --> 00:09:36,458
Let her go!
Don't hurt Kiriha.

146
00:09:36,541 --> 00:09:40,208
[KUKURI] And in exchange?
What will you do for me?

147
00:09:42,041 --> 00:09:43,708
[KIRIHA groans]

148
00:09:43,791 --> 00:09:46,375
[KAZUYA]
Okay. Fine.

149
00:09:46,458 --> 00:09:50,166
I accept your offer.
I'll be your malison cleanser.

150
00:09:50,250 --> 00:09:53,833
That's what you want, right?
Then please put Kiriha down.

151
00:09:53,916 --> 00:09:57,375
[KUKURI] Very well. You will
be held to those words.

152
00:09:57,458 --> 00:09:58,750
Kazuya...

153
00:09:58,833 --> 00:09:59,875
[KIRIHA grunts]

154
00:09:59,958 --> 00:10:01,416
[KAZUYA]
Kiriha!

155
00:10:03,166 --> 00:10:09,916
[KAZUYA] Kiriha!
Are you hurt? Talk to me.

156
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:13,416
I am fine, but thou art a fool.

157
00:10:13,500 --> 00:10:14,916
[KAZUYA]
Ah...

158
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:18,416
[KUKURI] Mm. And so,
this matter is settled.

159
00:10:18,500 --> 00:10:20,458
Just as it should have been.

160
00:10:20,541 --> 00:10:25,500
I have high hopes for you,
my new malison cleanser.

161
00:10:25,583 --> 00:10:27,041
[KAZUYA]
Ah--!

162
00:10:36,291 --> 00:10:38,958
[KUKURI]
Uh...

163
00:10:39,041 --> 00:10:40,500
[KIRIHA, KAZUYA]
Uh--!

164
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:44,750
[KIRIHA]
<i>Tsugumomo</i> !

165
00:10:47,625 --> 00:10:49,500
[KUKURI]
This here's <i>Tsugumomo</i> !

166
00:11:00,250 --> 00:11:04,208
[KUKURI]
Uh... Uhhh...

167
00:11:04,291 --> 00:11:08,500
No! Don't look at me!

168
00:11:08,583 --> 00:11:10,875
[KIRIHA laughs]

169
00:11:10,958 --> 00:11:13,500
You look like a
little brat now! Ha!

170
00:11:13,583 --> 00:11:15,000
[KIRIHA laughs]

171
00:11:15,083 --> 00:11:16,791
[KIRIHA] I knew that was why
you were wearing that mask!

172
00:11:16,875 --> 00:11:19,375
You're as weak as a
newborn babe without it!

173
00:11:19,458 --> 00:11:21,541
[KIRIHA laughs]

174
00:11:21,625 --> 00:11:23,958
You shrank too,
so stop makin' fun of me!

175
00:11:24,041 --> 00:11:25,291
[KIRIHA]
No, no, no.

176
00:11:25,375 --> 00:11:28,375
[KUKURI yelps]

177
00:11:28,458 --> 00:11:31,291
[KIRIHA chuckles]

178
00:11:31,375 --> 00:11:32,583
Hey, give it back.

179
00:11:32,666 --> 00:11:33,958
[KIRIHA] Why, so you
can make sport of me

180
00:11:34,041 --> 00:11:35,625
like you did before?

181
00:11:35,708 --> 00:11:37,208
[KUKURI yelps]

182
00:11:37,291 --> 00:11:39,583
[KUKURI] L-Look here. I had a
perfectly good reason for that.

183
00:11:39,666 --> 00:11:42,500
I'm sure you did, Kukuri,
and you can tell me

184
00:11:42,583 --> 00:11:44,958
all about it,
once I've gotten even.

185
00:11:45,041 --> 00:11:47,041
No. You wouldn't.
I'm a goddess, dang it!

186
00:11:47,125 --> 00:11:49,833
You do not want
to incur my wrath!

187
00:11:49,916 --> 00:11:54,125
I'll show you wrath!
Take this!

188
00:11:54,208 --> 00:11:57,416
What, you don't like that? Well
then, why don't we try this?

189
00:11:57,500 --> 00:11:58,958
[KUKURI] You're exposing
my unmentionables!

190
00:11:59,041 --> 00:12:00,875
[KIRIHA] Come on.
Just a little more.

191
00:12:00,958 --> 00:12:03,583
Snap, you stupid little brat!

192
00:12:06,833 --> 00:12:10,250
If you're to be believed...
then the entire point

193
00:12:10,333 --> 00:12:13,083
of that battle was to
get Kazuya to command me.

194
00:12:13,166 --> 00:12:16,875
Darn straight. I was never
actually gonna kill him.

195
00:12:16,958 --> 00:12:19,500
What with my divinity dryin' up,
I was in a real pickle.

196
00:12:19,583 --> 00:12:22,625
A good Tsugumomo wielder
is just what I need.

197
00:12:22,708 --> 00:12:24,250
It's a dangerous gig, though.

198
00:12:24,333 --> 00:12:26,500
So, I knew that you'd
be against him doing it.

199
00:12:26,583 --> 00:12:29,791
The only solution was to
have him become your master.

200
00:12:29,875 --> 00:12:31,750
So, yeah. I gave
him a little nudge

201
00:12:31,833 --> 00:12:33,708
to make sure he'd
have to use ya.

202
00:12:33,791 --> 00:12:35,750
Little more than a nudge,
don't ya think?

203
00:12:35,833 --> 00:12:37,666
[KUKURI] Once you've been
commanded by your true name,

204
00:12:37,750 --> 00:12:39,833
you have to do whatever
you're told to do.

205
00:12:39,916 --> 00:12:42,958
So the only one I had to win
over was Kazuya here!

206
00:12:43,041 --> 00:12:44,583
[KIRIHA groans]

207
00:12:44,666 --> 00:12:46,541
And whaddaya know,
my plan worked.

208
00:12:46,625 --> 00:12:48,708
Now I'm the boss
of both of you.

209
00:12:48,791 --> 00:12:50,541
[KUKURI laughs]

210
00:12:50,625 --> 00:12:53,958
[KIRIHA]
You dirty pest!

211
00:12:56,666 --> 00:12:58,583
[KAZUYA]
Calm down, Kiriha!

212
00:12:58,666 --> 00:13:00,000
[CHISATO]
She's just a kid!

213
00:13:00,083 --> 00:13:02,125
[KUKURI]
I am not! I'm ancient!

214
00:13:02,208 --> 00:13:03,750
Please stop
spinning the goddess.

215
00:13:03,833 --> 00:13:08,375
[KUKURI] Don't just ask her!
Do something! Aah!

216
00:13:08,458 --> 00:13:11,750
[KUKURI groans]

217
00:13:11,833 --> 00:13:13,291
There.

218
00:13:21,083 --> 00:13:22,750
Well. My house is this way.

219
00:13:22,833 --> 00:13:26,250
Thanks, Chisato. I'll try
to make it up to you later.

220
00:13:26,333 --> 00:13:30,250
Sorry about all the trouble,
Chisato. We'll see you tomorrow.

221
00:13:30,333 --> 00:13:31,791
[CHISATO]
Mm.

222
00:13:36,458 --> 00:13:38,958
[KIRIHA]
Mm...

223
00:13:39,041 --> 00:13:40,583
[KAZUYA]
Hey, Kiriha?

224
00:13:40,666 --> 00:13:42,541
[KIRIHA]
Uh?

225
00:13:42,625 --> 00:13:45,791
About this malison
cleanser thing.

226
00:13:45,875 --> 00:13:49,500
I know I was kind of
forced into it.

227
00:13:49,583 --> 00:13:51,791
But I still wanna
do a good job.

228
00:13:51,875 --> 00:13:54,041
[KIRIHA]
Mm.

229
00:13:54,125 --> 00:13:57,208
[KAZUYA] So I'm gonna
need your help, okay?

230
00:13:57,291 --> 00:13:58,750
[KIRIHA]
Aye.

231
00:14:01,750 --> 00:14:04,583
[KOKUYOU slurps]

232
00:14:04,666 --> 00:14:06,125
[KUKURI]
Hm.

233
00:14:07,833 --> 00:14:09,750
[KAZUYA] I guess
we should go now.

234
00:14:09,833 --> 00:14:11,458
[KUKURI]
See ya later!

235
00:14:15,208 --> 00:14:17,041
--[KIRIHA] Kukuri.
--[KUKURI] Huh?

236
00:14:18,541 --> 00:14:22,666
You can't let it
slip any further.

237
00:14:22,750 --> 00:14:24,333
I've got this.

238
00:14:30,416 --> 00:14:33,333
I wonder. Is this
truly for the best?

239
00:14:33,416 --> 00:14:39,083
Couldn't tell ya, but what's
done is done; let's trust him.

240
00:14:39,166 --> 00:14:40,875
[KUKURI sighs]

241
