right in front of us.

242
00:14:46,541 --> 00:14:48,000
Indeed.

243
00:14:51,416 --> 00:14:54,791
[KOKUYOU] The place is
certainly well ventilated now.

244
00:14:54,875 --> 00:14:56,416
[KUKURI]
No doubt.

245
00:15:00,041 --> 00:15:04,000
[KAZUYA] 
Hm. You really did shrink.

246
00:15:04,083 --> 00:15:06,333
[KIRIHA groans]

247
00:15:06,416 --> 00:15:10,125
And what if I have!
Who cares? You pissant!

248
00:15:10,208 --> 00:15:13,000
I shan't remain like this
forever, but it will take

249
