I'm completely restored.

250
00:15:15,708 --> 00:15:18,583
I'd better check and see
if you were injured at all.

251
00:15:20,791 --> 00:15:23,750
Do not treat me
like a child.

252
00:15:23,833 --> 00:15:27,375
[KAZUYA] Fine. As long
as you're not hurt.

253
00:15:27,458 --> 00:15:30,125
Are you really
that concerned?

254
