Yeah, of course I'm
worried about you.

255
00:15:32,375 --> 00:15:36,666
[KIRIHA] Mm. In that case, you'd
best take a nice, thorough look.

256
00:15:36,750 --> 00:15:39,000
[KAZUYA] Oh, no,
I don't think so.

257
00:15:40,625 --> 00:15:42,250
[KIRIHA sighs]

258
00:15:42,333 --> 00:15:44,125
I guess this is okay.

259
00:15:44,208 --> 00:15:47,666
Get over it. You're the one
who wanted to take a look at me.

260
00:15:47,750 --> 00:15:49,208
[KAZUYA sighs]

261
